results.title: S.H.I.E.L.D. (2010 - 2011)
results.description: One of the most complex and ambitious series ever published, S.H.I.E.L.D. explores the secret history of the world's premiere peacekeeping organization, featuring classic Marvel characters as well as real world figures like Leonardo da Vinci and Isaac Newton. It's like nothing you've ever seen!
